desc_short	-----								The Last Tinker is a joyous action adventure inspired by classics such as Jak & Daxter and Banjo Kazooie. Koru, a boy from the slums of Colortown, must rise from his roots to tackle the Bleakness, a dark force intent on wiping out joy. Koru must use color and emotion to restore life to Colortown!							
developer									Mimimi Productions								
